{"tid":2060364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟不景氣？中國微博徵網軍 留言一條最低剩「二毛」","createTime":"2020-06-11T14:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T15:08:31.000Z","uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1e730087a024ea58838db59f563dafaf4c190035","tid":2060364,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:49:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">經濟不景氣？中國微博徵網軍 留言一條最低剩「二毛」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國「五毛」惡名昭彰，指受僱傭發表有利於中國政府或相關部門評論的網路評論員。普通網民常以「五毛」、「五毛黨」稱之，諷刺其發一條評論就為了賺5毛酬勞。不過，近日網路出現中國徵才文，每一條回覆最低竟僅剩下2毛酬勞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3195097?fbclid=IwAR026y2EPasft5Wn3eFOrPxXCcoGpEasxMSKjsg0TQuzOqsiFbrKVYj7Bno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3195097%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR026y2EPasft5Wn3eFOrPxXCcoGpEasxMSKjsg0TQuzOqsiFbrKVYj7Bno&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0qbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=9e3e51bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3195097%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR026y2EPasft5Wn3eFOrPxXCcoGpEasxMSKjsg0TQuzOqsiFbrKVYj7Bno&h=26915581\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3195097?fbclid=IwAR026y2EPasft5Wn3eFOrPxXCcoGpEasxMSKjsg0TQuzOqsiFbrKVYj7Bno</a>"},{"pid":"be2c2251d37812be5ff88a541524f4e249cba9ba","tid":2060364,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a83d8ef0b4601d708c682beb831b511ceb95bfc","tid":2060364,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無耐之前先話五毛加左薪變七毛"},{"pid":"ed31519b49148c9f2a39c76b6341b3122537